@page
<style>
    body, .cassandra-slide * {
        font-family: 'Quicksand', Arial, sans-serif;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .cassandra-slide {
        background: #fafaff;
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 32px 0 rgba(123,110,246,0.08);
        display: flex;
        align-items: stretch;
        min-height: 380px;
        margin: 48px auto 48px auto;
        max-width: 980px;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-content {
        flex: 1.2;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: flex-start;
        padding: 56px 48px 56px 56px;
        background: transparent;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-title {
        color: #7b6ef6;
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        font-family: 'Quicksand', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-content p {
        color: #23223a;
        font-size: 1.18rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        text-align: left;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-content b {
        font-weight: 700;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-logo {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #f4f3fd;
        border-top-right-radius: 24px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 24px;
        min-width: 320px;
        min-height: 320px;
        max-width: 380px;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 32px 0 rgba(123,110,246,0.10);
        margin: 0;
    }
    .cassandra-slide-logo img {
        max-width: 180px;
        max-height: 140px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px 0 rgba(123,110,246,0.13);
        background: #fff;
        object-fit: contain;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    media (max-width: 900px) {
        .cassandra-slide {
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: unset;
            max-width: 98vw;
        }
        .cassandra-slide-content {
            padding: 36px 18px 24px 18px;
        }
        .cassandra-slide-logo {
            border-radius: 0 0 24px 24px;
            min-width: unset;
            min-height: 180px;
            max-width: 100vw;
            padding: 18px 0;
        }
    }
</style>
<div class="cassandra-slide">
    <div class="cassandra-slide-content">
        <div class="cassandra-slide-title">Giới thiệu về Apache Cassandra</div>
        <p><b>Apache Cassandra</b> là cơ sở dữ liệu NoSQL, xử lý dữ liệu lớn phân tán.</p>
        <p>Được dùng bởi Netflix, Facebook, Instagram để đảm bảo hệ thống ổn định.</p>
        <p>Thiết kế cho lưu trữ hàng tỷ tin nhắn mỗi ngày.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cassandra-slide-logo">
        <img src="/images/cassandra.png" alt="Cassandra logo" />
    </div>
</div>
